1.pipes can accept 1 or more parameters

2.bulitin pipes accepts parameters
//in component.html
<div> {{currencyExample | currency : 'USA'}} </div>
display the currency with dollar sign
<div> {{dateExample | date : 'MMM-dd-yy'}} </div>
displays:NOV 25 2021
  -currency
  -date
    -'MMM-dd-yyyy'
    -short
    -long
   -percentage
     -displays how many numbers displayed before and after zero
    <div> {{percentageExample | precent: '3.1-1'}} </div>
     (<beforedecimal><afterdecimal><maximum_to_display>)

3.syntax for writing parameter pipes
 {{<data_inputs> | <pipe_name> : <parameter>}}
